back country
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the high country beyond S.I. river gorges, as opposed to front down and plains land in front of the gorges and ranges.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
